what you want.

01:16:50.556 --> 01:16:53.559
She is all yours...

01:16:53.559 --> 01:16:55.561
When I have
what I want!

01:16:55.561 --> 01:16:57.062
Now where is it?

01:16:58.564 --> 01:16:59.565
Nearby.

01:16:59.565 --> 01:17:01.567
You've been told
to bring it with you.

01:17:01.567 --> 01:17:06.071
I've never been one
to do what I was told.

01:17:06.071 --> 01:17:08.073
Didn't Julie
tell you that?

01:17:10.576 --> 01:17:12.077
