underestimate me,

01:17:12.077 --> 01:17:13.078
My dear.

01:17:18.582 --> 01:17:20.584
I do have
something for you.

01:17:23.587 --> 01:17:24.588
What is it?

01:17:49.112 --> 01:17:52.115
A gamesman
to the very end.

01:17:54.117 --> 01:17:56.118
Oh, I admire that.

01:17:56.118 --> 01:17:59.622
