run, you fool!

01:20:32.768 --> 01:20:34.269
Get her!

01:20:35.771 --> 01:20:37.272
She went this way.

01:20:37.272 --> 01:20:40.275
Go, man!
Down in the field!

01:20:40.275 --> 01:20:42.277
Go, man!

01:20:42.277 --> 01:20:44.278
Catch her. Catch her.

01:20:51.285 --> 01:20:52.286
Do you see her?

01:20:52.286 --> 01:20:53.287
Only her blanket.

01:21:00.293 --> 01:21:01.294
Is that her?

01:21:01.294 --> 01:21:03.797
I don't see
any sign of her.

01:21:09.302 --> 01:21:10.804
That's all?

01:21:11.304 --> 01:21:12.305
Yes!

01:21:13.807 --> 01:21:14.307
Come back.

01:21:14.808 --> 01:21:16.309
But she must
be here somewhere.

01:21:16.810 --> 01:21:17.811
Come back.

01:21:49.340 --> 01:21:50.341
Hello, Julie.

01:21:53.344 --> 01:21:54.846
It's been
a long time.

01:21:57.348 --> 01:21:59.350
Please.

01:21:59.350 --> 01:22:01.352
I'm not Julie.

01:22:01.352 --> 01:22:03.354
You're not?

01:22:04.355 --> 01:22:05.857
No.

01:22:05.857 --> 01:22:07.357
I'm an actress.

01:22:07.357 --> 01:22:10.861
This was all arranged
by Dr. Lewis.

01:22:12.863 --> 01:22:15.365
Your sister's dead.

01:22:19.369 --> 01:22:20.370
Is she?

01:22:20.370 --> 01:22:21.872
Yes.

01:22:21.872 --> 01:22:23.373
I can prove it to you.

01:22:23.373 --> 01:22:24.374
Just come with me
to the attic.

01:22:24.374 --> 01:22:25.375
I'll show you
her body.

01:22:25.876 --> 01:22:28.878
You want me to come
to the attic with you?

01:22:28.878 --> 01:22:30.880
Yes, please,
before they come back.

01:22:33.382 --> 01:22:35.384
Why should I trust you?

01:22:35.384 --> 01:22:37.887
Just look at me.

01:22:37.887 --> 01:22:38.888
Listen to me.

01:22:38.888 --> 01:22:40.389
Can't you see
I'm not her?

01:22:45.393 --> 01:22:48.897
[Shouting]

01:22:48.897 --> 01:22:50.398
Poor Julie.

01:22:50.899 --> 01:22:52.901
Still playing
make-Believe.

01:23:32.438 --> 01:23:33.940
