01:23:58.964 --> 01:23:59.965
I'm sure she is,

01:23:59.965 --> 01:24:03.969
But that's not
the girl I saw.

01:24:05.470 --> 01:24:07.973
Look, why don't you

01:24:07.973 --> 01:24:08.974
Just give us
the address.

01:24:08.974 --> 01:24:10.475
We'll go there
ourselves.

01:24:10.475 --> 01:24:11.476
I can't do that.

01:24:11.476 --> 01:24:13.978
What is wrong
with you people?!

01:24:13.978 --> 01:24:16.480
She said they were
going to kill her!

01:24:16.480 --> 01:24:18.983
Christ, they
cut off her finger!

01:24:21.485 --> 01:24:22.486
Oh.

01:24:22.486 --> 01:24:24.989
Oh, get in. Get in!

01:24:24.989 --> 01:24:26.490
She's in here.

01:24:26.490 --> 01:24:29.994
She's been here
the whole time.

01:24:29.994 --> 01:24:31.995
Come on. Move! Move!

01:24:31.995 --> 01:24:33.496
I don't pay you
for that!

01:24:33.997 --> 01:24:34.998
Evelyn.

01:24:35.999 --> 01:24:37.500
Evelyn.

01:24:38.501 --> 01:24:40.003
Evelyn.

01:24:47.010 --> 01:24:49.012
Finished playing
in the snow?

01:24:49.012 --> 01:24:51.014
Your sister
is a resourceful woman.

01:24:51.014 --> 01:24:53.516
My sister's a fool,

01:24:54.017 --> 01:24:55.018
And so are
the two of you.

01:24:55.518 --> 01:24:57.020
I'll find her myself.

01:24:57.020 --> 01:24:59.022
Quickly.
Keep them apart.

01:24:59.022 --> 01:25:00.023
You shouldn't
wander around

01:25:00.023 --> 01:25:01.024
Up there
all by yourself.

01:25:01.524 --> 01:25:02.025
I mean,
it's a pretty old house,

01:25:02.525 --> 01:25:03.026
And you don't know
your way around,

01:25:03.526 --> 01:25:04.527
So why don't you
go back down there

01:25:04.527 --> 01:25:06.029
And let me look for her.

01:25:06.029 --> 01:25:07.029
You must trust me.

01:25:07.029 --> 01:25:08.529
You know, trust.
You hear?

01:25:08.529 --> 01:25:11.032
That's the foundation
of relationships...

01:25:18.539 --> 01:25:21.042
I'll find her.
I really will.

01:25:21.042 --> 01:25:22.543
See, there's no back
stairs to this house.

01:25:22.543 --> 01:25:24.045
It's the only way
she could get out.

01:25:24.045 --> 01:25:27.548
Oh, I'll find her,
wherever she is.

01:25:27.548 --> 01:25:29.550
There isn't a place to hide
in this house

01:25:29.550 --> 01:25:31.052
That I don't know about.

01:25:31.052 --> 01:25:32.053
Oh, yes.

01:25:32.053 --> 01:25:34.055
No, please.

01:25:34.055 --> 01:25:36.557
If we do find her,
you let me handle her.

01:25:36.557 --> 01:25:38.059
Dr. Lewis wants you
to stay away from her.

01:25:38.559 --> 01:25:41.062
Oh, he's been so worried
about things recently.

01:25:41.062 --> 01:25:42.063
Sometimes people worry

01:25:42.063 --> 01:25:43.564
When they really
don't have anything

01:25:43.564 --> 01:25:44.564
To worry about at all.

01:25:44.564 --> 01:25:45.565
I learned
a long time ago

01:25:45.565 --> 01:25:48.068
That worrying
doesn't help one bit.

01:25:56.576 --> 01:25:57.577
Miss McGovern.

01:25:58.078 --> 01:25:59.578
There.

01:25:59.578 --> 01:26:01.580
Oh.

01:26:01.580 --> 01:26:03.582
Where can she be?

01:26:05.084 --> 01:26:08.087
She wouldn't
go back in here, would she?

01:26:17.596 --> 01:26:18.597
Evelyn.

01:26:18.597 --> 01:26:20.598
Look, you stay right
against that door.

01:26:20.598 --> 01:26:22.100
You just stay there.

01:26:23.601 --> 01:26:25.103
Oh.

01:26:25.103 --> 01:26:29.107
Oh, she has caused
so much trouble.

01:26:29.107 --> 01:26:31.109
I, for one, am going
to be very glad

01:26:31.109 --> 01:26:32.110
When you've killed her,

01:26:32.110 --> 01:26:33.611
And this is
all over with.

01:26:33.611 --> 01:26:38.116
After what she's done,
I could kill her myself!

01:26:39.117 --> 01:26:41.619
She's got to be here
somewhere.

01:26:41.619 --> 01:26:42.620
Hmm?

01:26:43.121 --> 01:26:45.123
So, how do you
plan to do it?

01:26:45.623 --> 01:26:46.124
A rope?

01:26:46.624 --> 01:26:47.625
A knife?

01:26:47.625 --> 01:26:50.628
Oh, you don't
have to tell me.

01:26:51.129 --> 01:26:52.629
I was just curious.

01:26:53.130 --> 01:26:54.131
If you don't mind,

01:26:54.631 --> 01:26:57.633
I do have a suggestion.

01:26:57.633 --> 01:27:00.636
Use a piece of cord--
Strong, nylon cord.

01:27:01.137 --> 01:27:02.138
That's what I'd use.

01:27:02.138 --> 01:27:04.140
There's no blood.

01:27:05.641 --> 01:27:07.143
You know...

01:27:09.145 --> 01:27:10.646
Aah!

01:27:27.163 --> 01:27:28.664
[Footstep]

01:27:31.167 --> 01:27:32.667
Miss McGovern?

01:27:36.171 --> 01:27:37.672
Miss McGovern.

01:28:24.217 --> 01:28:26.219
Dr. Lewis?

01:28:26.219 --> 01:28:27.720
Did you find her?

01:28:37.229 --> 01:28:41.233
Mr. Murray is still
looking for her,

01:28:41.233 --> 01:28:42.734
But she's obviously
not in the house.

01:28:43.235 --> 01:28:44.235
She has to be.

01:28:44.235 --> 01:28:45.736
We'll find her.

01:28:45.736 --> 01:28:48.239
The two of you
have let her escape.

01:28:49.740 --> 01:28:50.741
Impossible.

01:28:51.742 --> 01:28:53.744
She must be here.

01:28:56.247 --> 01:28:57.748
I'm going home.

01:28:57.748 --> 01:29:00.251
[Piano plays]

01:29:08.259 --> 01:29:10.261
Call me...

01:29:12.263 --> 01:29:14.765
Call me
when you find her...

01:29:14.765 --> 01:29:16.267
If you find her.

01:29:16.267 --> 01:29:17.768
We have found her...

01:29:18.269 --> 01:29:19.270
Miss McGovern!

01:30:12.820 --> 01:30:14.822
There's no way out.

01:30:17.325 --> 01:30:18.326
[Door locks]

01:30:29.336 --> 01:30:31.338
Oh!

01:30:31.838 --> 01:30:32.838
Ohh...

01:31:05.371 --> 01:31:07.373
Hunting weather.

01:31:07.373 --> 01:31:07.873
Hunting weather.

01:31:23.887 --> 01:31:26.390
I know what
the cold can do.

01:31:26.390 --> 01:31:27.891
I've seen it.

01:31:28.392 --> 01:31:30.894
It's only
a matter of time.

01:31:59.422 --> 01:32:00.423
Aah!

01:32:02.425 --> 01:32:03.926
Aah!

01:32:25.446 --> 01:32:28.449
There is nowhere to go,
miss McGovern.

01:33:42.520 --> 01:33:43.521
[Creak]

01:33:58.535 --> 01:34:01.538
[Creaking]

01:34:19.555 --> 01:34:22.057
It's all over.

01:34:24.059 --> 01:34:25.561
The game is over.

01:34:36.071 --> 01:34:37.573
Aah!

01:35:10.604 --> 01:35:11.605
[Snap]

01:35:22.615 --> 01:35:25.117
[Dragging trap along floor]

01:36:49.698 --> 01:36:51.199
Katie?

01:37:08.216 --> 01:37:10.217
Oh, Katie.
